data.description: Beautiful 2 story in Mill Creek Estates!  Great floor plan with open living spaces, modern finishes, granite countertops, SS appliances, timeless LVP flooring, ample storage space and the list goes on! Lovely primary suite with spa like bath and another bedroom located on the 1st floor! Game room and 2 more bedrooms upstairs! Nice outdoor space with covered patio and pool sized ready yard! Zoned to Magnolia ISD! Come see today!
